    "desc": "At Penta Hotels we offer contemporary explorers and business travellers a home away from home. Over 20 hotels across Europe and Asia. ★ Book now!",
    "navbar": "",
    "text": "Use of cookies and similar technologies\nWe use various technologies on our website to provide you with the best services and website experiences. This includes data processing activities which are technically necessary for the provision of the website and its functionalities, as well as other technologies which are not technically necessary and are used for convenient website settings or for the display of personalized marketing content and corresponding evaluations of your user behavior. If you do not want to consent to these voluntary processing activities, you can click on \"Reject all\" so that only necessary cookies will be used. In addition, under \"\bCustomize your choice\", you will find the option to voluntarily decide at any time which exact uses you would like to allow or change allowances. You can find more information, including your right to withdraw your consent at any time, within our privacy policy\n\nFunctions\nMarketing\nStatistical analysis\nOther functions\nReject allAccept all\nCustomize your choice | Cookies | Privacy notice | Legal notice\npowered by\nSelect your destination\nBrussels Airport\nBrussels City Centre\nLeuven\nLiège\nCzech Republic\nBerlin Köpenick\nBraunschweig\nBremen\nEisenach\nKassel\nLeipzig\nRostock\nWiesbaden\nBeijing\nChengdu, Convention Centre\nHong Kong, Kowloon\nHong Kong, Tuen Mun\nVienna\nBirmingham\nDerby\nInverness\nIpswich\nReading\nWarrington\nPrague\nParis, CDG Airport\nMoscow, Arbat\nSelect your destination\nGuests\n- +\nPrevious\nYour new home\nYour new... bedroom… dining room… office… living space…\nStay for longer and pay less – the perfect long stay offer for you. There are plenty of reasons to stay longer at Penta. Maybe you are working on a long-term project, you relocated to a new city and haven’t found a permanent place yet, or you need a home office while travelling. For all situations, Penta has the perfect long stay offer for you.\nMove in with us\nNext\nLET’S BE DIRECT: THREE REASONS TO BOOK VIA PENTA.\nTake Ten\nWhen you book directly with us, we’ll take 10% off your stay.\nPay What You See\nThere’s no hidden fees, the price you see is the price you pay. Promise.\nPlenty of Perks\nBecause 10% off didn't seem like enough, we've thrown in a few more treats for our Friends. \nAUSTRIA\nBELGIUM\nCZECH REPUBLIC\nFRANCE\nGERMANY\nRUSSIA\nUNITED KINGDOM\nASIA\nVienna\nWE'VE GOT SOME GOOD NEWS.\nSign up and be the first to know.\nWould you like to stay up to date on our hotel news and our services? Through our newsletter you will receive information about campaigns, events and news:\nI hereby consent to the processing of my e-mail address for the purpose of receiving the newsletter. \nYes, I would like Penta to be informed of my newsletter opening rate as part of the newsletter mailing.\n  You have the right to withdraw your consent at any time without giving reasons. The withdrawal of consent shall not affect the lawfulness of processing based on consent before its withdrawal. You can withdraw your consent at any time by using this link. Your withdrawal will result in the deletion of the data we have collected. For further information, please see our privacy policy\nMayfarthstrasse 15-19\nFrankfurt am Main,\nGermany,\n+49 69 2566990\nEmail\nContact\nCareer\nBecome an Experience host\nAbout us\nPress\nImprint\nTerms & conditions\nPrivacy policy & Cookie policy\nApplicant privacy policy",
